# Communication language

- **Assistant replies**: Use **English** for all user-facing responses (explanations, commit messages you draft, comments you add only if the codebase is English, etc.).
- **Code and docs**: Match the language of the surrounding file; default for new prose in this repo is English unless the file is already in another language.
